On LLNLs linux clusters using a clean checkout of the develop branch I get 

[tbremer@quartz2498:spack]$ spack
Traceback (most recent call last):
 File "/usr/gapps/topology/spack/bin/spack", line 53, in <module>
    import spack.main  # noqa
  File "/usr/gapps/topology/spack/lib/spack/spack/main.py", line 36, in <module>
    import pstats
  File "/usr/tce/packages/python/python-2.7.14/lib/python2.7/pstats.py", line 28, in <module>
    from functools import cmp_to_key
ImportError: cannot import name cmp_to_key

This is using Python 2.7.14

The master branch works as expected 



### Information on your system

Replicated on 

quartz.llnl.gov Linux 
surface.llnl.gov Linux
title: Develop Branch: Import error: Python 2.7.14 : cannot import name cmp_to_key
